{"tid":244883,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)狼人-盧根","createTime":"2017-05-15T18:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T19:58:04.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b5749d49a5c19513acbbcb2f38c1ee07966ac9","tid":244883,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0057fd01\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7772516b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1a494af6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/03/10/1999521_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F1999521_1.jpg&h=795ec1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2029年，一個變種人所剩無幾的年代。羅根在自己租來的車子裡被外面的聲響吵醒，下車後發現四個小偷在拆車輪要拿去賣。昏沉的羅根打算勸離他們，不料其中一個小偷直接向他開槍，羅根中槍後出爪反抗，更因小偷射損車身而在盛怒之下失手殺了他們所有人。<br />\n現在的羅根是當隨車司機來餬口。當天早上，他如往常一樣賄賂醫院職員以替查爾斯取藥。回到車上後，發現有一位類似政府官員的人坐在車上，並遞給他名片表示自己的名字是皮爾斯，在一個名叫「阿卡利」的公司裡效力，且說出昨天羅根的暴行、查爾斯的能力已經逐漸失控且被盯上與自己要一個女孩，羅根說他不曉得有什麼女孩後，強硬的要他下車，自己也識相的下車離開了..<br />\n<br />\n2 40AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37b703ec81de3a46a5c9875b2a3ff0a93b9e64a","tid":244883,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8967da24387a7e3d68f389d7ca7d0eed4d91c10","tid":244883,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f58fb3b8bfd7eb95dec359a9f9cf2767aec5a08","tid":244883,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffa5c1f06185f7b6a000888cd733720336ff1ed","tid":244883,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}